      "name": "Autres informations",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "textual_research",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "audios": [
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations91667",
                    "name": "CN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/80b0e526a02c719facf6eda12c12816b_3675062951558974804.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations91746",
                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/6c71bef7de17d8b89d5ebf48c869651d_1007978840071197136.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations7694",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/2290378e4d1b120ad6a29dc4cdc34714_992966531685167695.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations55009",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/d0bd633e1ca03e04f3b6175a7cd91507_2039654283206745339.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Une affaire de meurtre s&#39;est déroulée pendant la première représentation de Lyney et Lynette au grand Opéra. Bien qu&#39;ils aient été innocentés des accusations portées contre eux, leur identité d&#39;agents du Foyer de l&#39;âtre a été révélée.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Charlotte : Vous avez vaincu l&#39;Archon Hydro lors de votre tout premier procès à l&#39;Opéra. C&#39;est incroyable, ça va rester dans les annales.</span></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/14/29705491/8623c8d144e47a23c390bf7694c63018_7986617543368815907.png",
                "title": "Indice pertinent - Opéra : Défense de Lyney"
              },
              {
                "audios": [
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations18231",
                    "name": "CN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/1387bd6078194235eb1af92a80e2863e_2593674182563488418.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations83900",
                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/3a4189c4c7270a00d9d9f70e9ae4911b_1110101879246729472.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations49791",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/5287ccd65f089a234f47ec565535529c_7852168251319266.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations46144",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/6ac9b40e55a8e338c38c492aecf7b9ed_2642196991133216842.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Il s&#39;avère que les Fontainois peuvent être dissous par l&#39;eau de la mer primordiale. Au fil des années, Vacher a kidnappé et dissous de nombreuses jeunes filles pour tenter de trouver un moyen de ramener sa femme dissoute.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Charlotte : Je ne m&#39;attendais pas à ce que vous réussissiez à résoudre l&#39;affaire sur laquelle j&#39;enquêtais depuis tout ce temps. Quelle heureuse coïncidence, vous ne trouvez pas ?</span></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/14/29705491/e5318a9719e199899c2559a69839726d_2777408164018438312.png",
                "title": "Indice pertinent - Opéra : Vérité de l'affaire des disparitions en série"
              },
              {
                "audios": [
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations57814",
                    "name": "CN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/bab57bd8aa4a6732520dfd6f5e962e26_7157308125016787063.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations48001",
                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/bce78ee31ee8ca95e7bf762c203893c1_7689999894354925045.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations7728",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/d771fa2d02546a5f6145fc2947d13901_6074719088617364622.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations60701",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/7b2605b1a44f00dba0f3cdab59184799_3089844536513915180.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bien que Neuvillette ait cru Tartaglia innocent, l&#39;Oratrice l&#39;a finalement jugé coupable, et même Furina ne savait pas pourquoi.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Charlotte : C&#39;est la première fois que monsieur Neuvillette et l&#39;Oratrice ne rendent pas le même verdict. Même l&#39;Archon Hydro ne comprend pas.</span></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/14/29705491/ce21cae48f37c74c8d1b6dbf7cba12af_7161598270788196478.png",
                "title": "Indice pertinent - Opéra : Conviction de Tartaglia"
              },
              {
                "audios": [
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations42322",
                    "name": "CN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/4ea586c1c02e7aed4c4540473a31d896_725122914139596880.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations84504",
                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/a7f8eb72a6c7e12e5006dd7fef721a4e_6671784273575853388.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations5588",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/35db32c0cfd7c44ef316f496c177a958_4112735788141832151.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations53816",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/0ed0f80b680c7d8278084e58df642cf5_4060833218373655410.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Au cours de la réunion diplomatique avec Arlecchino, elle a révélé qu&#39;elle avait déjà enquêté sur Furina et pensait qu&#39;il était possible que non seulement Furina ne soit pas vraiment l&#39;Archon, mais qu&#39;elle soit en fait affligée d&#39;une sorte de malédiction.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Charlotte : Une exécutrice des Fatui... C&#39;est vraiment quelqu&#39;un d&#39;extraordinaire, son jugement doit avoir de la valeur.</span></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/14/29705491/b0e8267595eb7de707fb32e64f03dace_2453608712211499910.png",
                "title": "Indice pertinent - Île d'Erinnyes : Rencontre avec Arlecchino"
              },
              {
                "audios": [
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations20263",
                    "name": "CN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/1156677b3cac6f321c840695aa3d1614_4255045214018808005.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations79653",
                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/f1cf1eb125eedfb062d8b4371f2abd4c_383955268097340931.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations73066",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/5aabe082eb89610c463ded3ee6e2397b_426248538623691834.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations37889",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/1169bcfcebf415ba09af3253c3fdab55_3536976489866606225.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">L&#39;entrée vers la mer primordiale est scellée sous la zone interdite de la Forteresse de Méropide, mais la mer a dernièrement failli se libérer. Elle ne fut que momentanément repoussée par la puissance de Neuvillette.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Charlotte : La Forteresse de Méropide a failli être détruite... En tant que journaliste, je regretterai toujours de ne pas avoir été témoin de cet événement.</span></p><p></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/14/29705491/6e795e0c7154797ecfca47a5f76e8adf_2499551148102605767.png",
                "title": "Indice pertinent - Forteresse de Méropide : Intrusion de ta mer primordiale dans la Forteresse de Méropide "
              },
              {
                "audios": [
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations87929",
                    "name": "CN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/17e49bef3e53dc63df35bc4b9b1ca9b9_4632754566230890193.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations42350",
                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/c24b35dadbdd0bb0272e1af5afeb2ed3_4630237321918935474.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations88576",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/e4614799079c3a4dc4444844d579edae_654020523530155187.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations66924",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/f112550c73aa38c911a843102594ea2b_3709992861890373828.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Dans un rêve, vous avez vu Tartaglia flotter dans la mer, ainsi qu&#39;une baleine d&#39;une taille indescriptible.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Charlotte : Selon monsieur Neuvillette, Tartaglia et cette baleine étaient tous les deux dans la mer primordiale à ce moment-là.</span></p>",
                "title": "Indice pertinent - Forteresse de Méropide : Baleine dans le rêve"
              },
              {
                "audios": [
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations3587",
                    "name": "CN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/5286fa8a9a42178468fa1298faa4b976_3462479584032004664.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations58549",
                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/91be4e1040f864cc19696ea5f6ce95ba_4446063867400543968.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations87628",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/2112010ee499521031b622095f6d7c06_6177852020815318460.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations49409",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/17f3d1c3db22039053af2a9c7b2e4693_8181095247904191343.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Alors que vous exploriez les ruines près du Village de Poisson, elles ont commencé à s&#39;effondrer et Navia est tombée dans un plan d&#39;eau contenant de l&#39;eau de la mer primordiale. Seule la protection des membres décédés de la Spina di Rosula a empêché sa dissolution.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Charlotte : J&#39;ai failli perdre une amie aussi précieuse que Navia. J&#39;en ai encore des frissons.</span></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/14/29705491/7af272e3d904d8f01abd197c55340e85_4898543620928760865.png",
                "title": "Indice pertinent - Ruines : Navia tombant dans l'eau"
              },
              {
                "audios": [
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations87268",
                    "name": "CN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/79a9c96ad5339b574ca727cb07cf1c85_7168995453972041521.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations91565",
                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/14/29705491/10ab8b181fba3d3fdbf70f766ab723d2_8545555324888852802.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations24191",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/441720384d72199174b02f1f0d641c05_7176373918411785677.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations66258",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/05/20/29705491/aa137e4f98951ba485a8f57b6b8b12ba_7556897798124223749.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">La sorcière N a communiqué avec vous en connectant vos consciences. Elle croit que la prophétie se réalisera, mais qu&#39;il ne faut pas abandonner tout espoir.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Charlotte : Les paroles de quelqu&#39;un d&#39;aussi extraordinaire qu&#39;une sorcière ne peuvent réellement être comprises que lorsque que que chose de surnaturel vous arrive.</span></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/14/29705491/6097983852fabd9062cf80b9534d2eaf_5119959739580303391.png",
                "title": "Indice pertinent - Cour de Fontaine : Goûteron avec la sorcière"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
